01:50:06.652 --> 01:50:08.404
Aren't you, Viktor?

01:50:08.487 --> 01:50:10.239
Oh, yes.

01:50:11.491 --> 01:50:13.076
Hi.

01:50:16.120 --> 01:50:18.080
